<h3 style="font-family: arial; font-size: large; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left;">
  Suggested Success Strategy
</h3>

<p style="font-family: arial; font-size: medium; text-align: left;">
  Regardless of your professional discipline, business is the engine that drives economic well-being. The economy continues to improve and job growth continues to look promising in 2017. You can help enhance your personal economic prospects by learning more about the business of business.
</p>

<p style="font-family: arial; font-size: medium; text-align: left;">
  <span style="font-weight: bold;">Goal:</span> Select one business book from the five pictured above, read it, practice its principles and shift your career into a higher gear in 2017. Of course, you can select all 18 books, read more than one per month, and receive a guaranteed seat in business class!
</p>

<p style="font-family: arial; font-size: medium; text-align: left;">
  <span style="font-weight: bold;"> NOTE:</span> The 18 Best Business Books of 2016 — those making at least three "Best of" lists — are being counted down on Twitter <a href="http://twitter.com/webapprentices" target="_blank"><b>@webapprentices</b></a> and on Facebook <a href="https://www.facebook.com/beantownweb/" target="_blank"><b>@beantownweb</b></a>.
</p>

